al; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">a)&nbsp;<i>Lactobacillus casei&nbsp;</i>dan&nbsp;<i>Lactobacillus\r\nbulgaricus,&nbsp;</i>untuk membuat&nbsp;</span><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">yoghurt.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">b)&nbsp;<i>Acetobacter xylinum,&nbsp;</i>untuk\r\nmembuat&nbsp;nata de coco<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">c)&nbsp;<i>Acetobacter,&nbsp;</i>untuk membuat asam\r\ncuka.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">d)&nbsp;<i>Streptococcus lactis,&nbsp;</i>untuk\r\nmembuat mentega.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">e)&nbsp;<i>Lactobacillus sp&nbsp;</i>untuk membuat\r\nterasi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">2) Bakteri penghasil antibiotik:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">a)&nbsp;<i>Streptomyces griceus,&nbsp;</i>penghasil&nbsp;&nbsp;streptomisin.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">b)&nbsp;<i>Stretomyces aureofacien,&nbsp;</i>penghasil\r\naureomisin.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">c)&nbsp;<i>Streptomyces venezuele,&nbsp;</i>penghasil\r\nkloramfenikol.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">3) Bakteri penyubur tanah:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">a)&nbsp;<i>Rhizobium leguminosarum&nbsp;</i>bersimbiosis<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pada akar tanaman\r\nkacang-kacangan dan dapat&nbsp;</span><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">mengikat nitrogen.&nbsp;</span><i style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Azetobacter</i><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">,&nbsp;</span><i style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Chlorococcum</i><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">,&nbsp;</span><i style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Clostridium&nbsp;</i><i style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">pasteurianum</span></i><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">,&nbsp;<i>Rhodospirillum &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;rubrum&nbsp;</i>yang hidup bebas dan&nbsp;</span><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">dapat mengikat nitrogen.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">b)&nbsp;<i>Nitrosomonas&nbsp;</i>dan&nbsp;<i>Nitrosococcus</i>,\r\ndapat mengubah amonia menjadi<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;nitrit,&nbsp;<i>dan\r\nNitrobacter</i>, dapat mengubah nitrit menjadi nitrat.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><b><i><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">b. Bakteri yang merugikan</span></i></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">1) Pada\r\nmanusia</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">a.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">a.Clostridium\r\ntetani menyebabkan penyakit Tetanus, berbentuk batang, tempat infeksi otot.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">b.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">b.Diplococcus pneumoniae menyebabkan penyakit Pneumonia,\r\nberbentuk bola, tempat infeksi Paru-paru<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">c.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">c.Mycobacterium tuberculois &nbsp;menyebabkan penyakit TBC, berbentuk batang,\r\ntempat infeksi paru-paru<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">d.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">d.Mycobacterium laprae menyebabkan penyakit Lepra,\r\nberbentuk batang, tempat infeksi kulit<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">e.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">e.Neisseria gonorrhoene menyebabkan penyakit Raja Singa,\r\nberbentuk Spiral, tempat infeksi Alat Kelamin<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">f.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">f.Pesteurella pestis menyebabkan penyakit Pes(sampar),\r\nberbentuk batang, tempat infeksi Kelenjar Darah<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">g.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">g.Salmonella typhosa menyebabkan penyakit Tipus,\r\nberbentuk batang, tempat infeksi Usus Halus<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">h.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">h.Shigella dysentriae menyebabkan penyakit Disentri,\r\nberbentuk batang, tempat infeksi Kelenjar Darah<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">i.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">i.Tryponema pallidium menyebabkan penyakit Sifilis,\r\nberbentuk Spiral, tempat infeksi Alat Kelamin<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">j.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">j.Vibrio\r\ncomma menyebabkan penyakit Kolera, berbentuk Koma, tempat infeksi Usus halus<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">2) Pada hewan<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">a)&nbsp;<i>Actynomices bovis</i>: bengkak rahang pada\r\nsapi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">b)&nbsp;<i>Bacillus anthraxis</i>: penyakit antraks\r\npada ternak.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">c)&nbsp;<i>Streptococcus</i>: radang payudara sapi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">d)&nbsp;<i>Cytopage columnaris</i>: penyakit pada\r\nikan.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">3) Pada tanaman<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">a)&nbsp;<i>Xanthomonas oryzae</i>: menyerang pucuk\r\nbatang padi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">b)&nbsp;<i>Xanthomonas campestris</i>: menyerang\r\ntanaman kubis.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">c)&nbsp;<i>Pseudomonas solanacearum</i>: layu pada\r\nterung-terungan.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">d)&nbsp;<i>Erwina carotovora</i>: busuk pada\r\nbuah-buahan.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">4) Yang merusak bahan makanan:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">a)&nbsp;<i>Acetobacter</i>: merubah etanol (alkohol)\r\nmenjadi asam cuka<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">sehingga merugikan perusahaan anggur.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">b)&nbsp;<i>Pseudomonas</i>: membentuk asam bongkrek\r\n(racun) pada tempe<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">bongkrek.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 12pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">c)&nbsp;<i>Clostridium botulinum</i>: penghasil racun\r\nmakanan.<br>\r\n</span><b style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN"><br></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 12pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><b style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-fareast-language:IN">GANGGANG BIRU</span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 12pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">merupakan\r\nganggang yang paling sederhana. Dalam beberapa hal, strukturnya mirip dengan\r\nsel bakteri sehingga sementara ahli ada yang menggunakan istilah bakteri hijau\r\nbiru (Cyanobacteria) untuk organisme tersebut. Sungguhpun demikian, organisme\r\ntersebut memiliki klorofil a sebagai organ fotosintesis yang berbeda dengan\r\nklorofil pada bakteri fotosintesis. Selain itu, ganggang tersebut juga\r\nmelepaskan O</span><sub style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">2</sub><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;sebagai hasil fotosintesis yang tidak dijumpai\r\npada bakteri. Alasan inilah yang menempatkan organisme tersebut dalam kelompok\r\ntersendiri, yaitu Cyanophyta.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;"><b><span style="font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">CIRI&nbsp;UMUM:</span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 5.25pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">Â·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Tipe\r\nsel: sel Prokariotik (sama dengan bakteri)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 5.25pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">Â·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Uniseluler\r\ndan Multiseluler<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 5.25pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">Â·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Memiliki\r\npigmen fikosianin<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 5.25pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">Â·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Klorofil\r\ntidak di dalam kloroplas, tetapi tersebar di seluruh sitoplasma<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;"><b><span style="font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">HABITAT GANGGANG BIRU</span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 5.25pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-fareast-language:IN">Â·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Perairan\r\n(terutama perairan tawar) dan tempat-tempat lembab.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;">Â·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mampu\r\nhidup pada perairan dengan suhu sampai 85 derajat C (sumber air panas) sehingga\r\nGanggang Biru merupakan salah satu vegetasi perintis.</span><br></span><br></p>');

